\s HIRYA Y’URUZI
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Hirya y’uruzi hariy’igihugu, igihugu gitemba amata n’ubuki, niyo ndaba niyo ndiko ndaja iyagisezeranye niyo yakimpishuriye.\bd*
\pc \bdit Ngenda ndirimba kandi nezerewe, nubwo ngendera mu muniho, kubw’\bdit*\bdit  Ivyiza \bdit*\bdit biri mu \bdit*\bdit Gihugu\bdit*\bdit , ntobigereranya n’ivy’iki gihe.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ninashika mur’ico gihugu, nzohanagurwa amarira yose, n’Umwami nyene ico gihugu, kand’azonyambika n’igitsibo.\bd*
\pc \bdit Ngenda ndirimba kandi nezerewe, nubwo ngendera mu muniho, kubw’ Ivyiza biri mu Gihugu, ntobigereranya n’ivy’iki gihe.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd N’igihugu c’abikiwe abahizi, abazonesha urugamba rukomeye, giteguriw’abera b’Imana, bavyawe n’\bd*\bd I\bd*\bd jambo na Mpwemu Yera.\bd*
\pc \bdit Ngenda ndirimba kandi nezerewe, nubwo ngendera mu muniho, kubw’ Ivyiza biri mu Gihugu, ntobigereranya n’ivy’iki gihe.\bdit*
